  <Annotation SID="4000">
    <P Name="Name">
Control strategy: Trigger criterion S_K
S_K combines wheel decceleration control with slip control 
using weighting factors  K_z and K_\lambda
S_K=K_z*z_R + K_\lambda * \lambda_{rel}
(see p.127 in M. Burckhardt 
Fahrwerktechnik:Radschlupfregelsysteme)
</P>
